phoon Omar|Lusing]] || Luming || Husing || Loleng || Katring || Luding || Lusing || [[Tropical Storm Zita (1997)|Luming]] || [[Typhoon Babs (1998)|Loleng]] || Luding || [[Typhoon Prapiroon (2000)|Lusing]] |- | Maring || Miling<ref name="Mill"/> || Miding || Mameng || Maring || Miling || Indang || Miding || Delang || Mameng || [[Typhoon Sally (1996)|Maring]] || Miling || Miding || [[Tropical Storm Wendy (1999)|Mameng]] || Maring |- | Ningning || Narsing || [[Typhoon Flo (1990)|Norming]]<ref name="PHP2"/> || [[Typhoon Kinna (1991)|Neneng]] || Ningning || Narsing || Luring || Norming || Esang || Naneng || Ningning || [[Typhoon Ivan|Narsing]] || [[Typhoon Faith (1998)|Norming]] || Naneng || Ningning |- | Osang || [[Typhoon Sarah (1989)|Openg]]<ref name="PHP"/> || [[Typhoon Gene|Oyang]] || Oniang || Osang || Openg || Monang || Oyang || Garding || Oniang || Osang || [[Tropical Storm Linda (1997)|Openg]] || || [[Typhoon Bart (1999)|Oniang]] || [[Typhoon Saomai (2000)|Osang]] |- | Paring || Pining || [[Typhoon Hattie (1990)|{{Not a typo|Pasing}}]] || [[Tropical Storm Luke (1991)|Pepang]] || Paring || Pining || Naning || Pasing || || Pepang || Paring || Pining || || Pepang || Paring |- | Reming || [[Typhoon Angela (1989)|Rubing]]<ref name="PHP"/> || [[Typhoon Mike|Ruping]] || [[Typhoon Mireille (1991)|Rosing]] || Reming || Rubing || Oning || || || [[Typhoon Angela|Rosing]] || Reming || [[Typhoon Paka|Rubing]] || || Rening || Reming |- | Seniang || [[Typhoon Dan (1989)|Saling]] || Susang || [[Typhoon Orchid (1991)|Sendang]] || [[Typhoon Gay (1992)|Seniang]] || Saling || Puring || || || Sendang || Seniang || || || Sendang || Seniang |- | Toyang || [[Typhoon Elsie (1989)|Tasing]]<ref name="PHP"/> || [[Typhoon Page (1990)|Tering]] || Trining || || [[Typhoon Yancy (1993)|Tasing]] || || || || Trining || Toyang || || || Trining || [[Tropical Storm Rumbia (2000)|Toyang]] |- | [[Typhoon Ruby (1988)|Unsang]] || Unsing || Uding || [[Tropical Storm Thelma|Uring]] || || Unsing || || || |